title: Limitations of porting existing DTK agents from Version 8 to Version 9 - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: The following is a list of limitations to be taken care of when porting existing DTK agents: All compilation errors must be resolved based on the latest generated code Classes that are no longer available in version 9: DRGeneratedFormContract.java DRAgentConfigData.java There are changes to the new generated code class structure. Some of which are no longer generated or supported. See Creating New Config Class for the supported code class structure.
